 art (sacral paintings, memorials, crosses and chapels), the wonders of nature (parks, lakes, rivers, rocks, hills and trees), museums, historical sites, etc. \n\nAbout the Author: Giedre Jankevichute is an art historian, a broad-minded academic and author of many publications in her field, who also happens to be a passionate and observant traveler.\nGraphic Designer: Isaac Zibuts\nPhotographers: A.Aleksandravicius, A. Baltenas, K. Driskius, V. Knya, A. Luksenas, Z. Nekrosius, R. Paknys, K. Stoskus, G. Treciokas, R. Urbakavicius.\nMaps: \'Briedis\' Publishers.',1),(449,NULL,NULL,'Kovo Vėjas','LT','Kovo',23,2011,'Vytautas Landsbergis',NULL,NULL,'LT023',NULL,'kovo-vejas','2016-12-23 22:01:26','2016-12-23 22:13:49',2,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(450,NULL,'978-3-8317-1959-4','Litauen : handbuch fur individuelles entdecken','DE','Reise Know-How',444,2011,'Gunther Schafer',NULL,NULL,'LT024',NULL,'litauen-handbuch-fur-individuelles-entdecken','2016-12-23 22:01:26','2016-12-23 23:49:33',2,'5133_2B7QZIjL.jpg','image/jpeg',44102,333,500,NULL,1),(451,NULL,'978-609-411-084-9','Lietuvių kalbos tyrinėjimo istorija 1980-2010 m.','LT','Lietuvių Kalbos Institutas',766,2012,'Algirdas Sabaliauskas',NULL,NULL,'LT025',NULL,'lietuviu-kalbos-tyrinejimo-istorija-1980-2010-m','2016-12-23 22:01:26','2016-12-23 22:13:49',2,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(452,NULL,'978-9955-718-06-2','Lietuva UNESCO. Lietuvos muziejai: žemėlapis 2012-2013','LT','Lietuvos nacionalinė UNESCO komisija',NULL,2012,'Sud. Laura Almantaitė, Audrius Stasiulaitis',NULL,NULL,'LT026',NULL,'lietuva-unesco-lietuvos-muziejai-zemelapis-2012-2013','2016-12-23 22:01:26','2016-12-23 22:13:49',2,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(453,NULL,'978-9955-545-08-8','Atsidusejimai','LT','Dialogo Kulturos Institutas',72,2003,'Tevas Stanislovas',NULL,NULL,'LT027',NULL,'atsidusejimai','2016-12-23 22:01:26','2016-12-23 23:49:36',2,'512dRyWQWTL.jpg','image/jpeg',36352,333,500,NULL,1),(454,'','978-609-8136-06-7','Vilnius Sculpture Walks'