iry tale to postmodern aesthetics. In the novel, the seven dwarves are men who live communally with Snow White and earn a living by washing buildings and making Chinese baby food. Snow White quotes Mao and the dwarves grapple with low self-esteem in this raucous retelling of the classic tale.',1),(1068,' 978-0330298636',NULL,'Love','EN','Picador',120,1988,'Angela Carter',NULL,NULL,'FIC127',NULL,'love','2016-12-23 22:01:29','2016-12-24 14:15:53',21,'41HC5GHESNL.jpg','image/jpeg',23796,314,475,'\"One day, Annabel saw the sun and moon in the sky at the same time.  The sight filled her with a terror which entirely consumed her … for she had no instinct for self-preservation if she was confronted by ambiguities.\"&lt;p&gt;Annabel and Lee are married; Lee and Buzz are brothers.  A quirky threesome, they have set up a household on the fringes on university life in the late sixties.  Their hermetic existence is filled with drugs, sex, alchohol, intensity, and madness; their relationships with one another are haunting and complex.&lt;p&gt;Carter\'s compelling tale carries echoes of Poe and Bronte into the very modern world of artists\' flats, psychiatrists\' offices, and generational conflicts.  It is ultimately a tale of the search for loyalty and love in the midst of emotional starvation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',1),(1069,'417060807',NULL,'334','EN','Methuen',260,1982,'Thomas M. Disch',NULL,NULL,'FIC128',NULL,'334','2016-12-23 22:01:29','2016-12-23 22:40:51',21,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(1070,'','','The Body Artist','EN','Picador',125,2002,'Don DeLillo','','','FIC129','','the-body-artist','2016-12-23 22:01:29','2017-06-12 13:44:48',21,'51i8sOCwt-L._SY344_BO1_204_203_200_.jpg','image/jpeg',22040,227,346,'',1),(1071,NULL,'978-0980226607','The Easy Chain','EN','Aurora148',502,2008,'Evan Dara',NULL,NULL,'FIC130',NULL,'the-easy-chain','2016-12-23 22:01:29','2016-12-23 23:54:09',21,'41JXEwI9BuL.jpg','image/jpeg',25886,334,500,'&lt;span id=\"caseCorrespondence_16477226785_text